{"title":"阔佬坐牢付费","authors":["池北偶华君武"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":2,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"阔佬坐牢付费"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗华君武画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报载，澳大利亚新南威尔士州州长打算制订新条例，要对有钱的囚犯收取５万澳元的坐牢费。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"财主大亨犯法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也度铁窗生涯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临时寄居监狱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比消闲度假。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管吃管穿管住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个铜板不花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班房岂能白坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未免便宜了他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既有大量钞票，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何不敲他一把。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"州长别出心裁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备土法上马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阔佬一律收钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按照宾馆计价。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫富区别对待，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是巧哉妙也。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}